Subject: drm/i915: Use REG_BIT() & co. for universal plane bits
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 12d7d858e63d0769a91aab218828e0526c0ab49d
